reviewText: Simply a number of boring strip shows.  Giving one star is because there is not an option of zero.
I was hoping for so much more coming from Teri. Sigh. I already resold it. Oh well.

I interviewed Terri for my television show.  She was amazing.  Beautiful, smart, funny and very sexy.  This DVD is amazing. I think my gay male lover is now straight.
I have never been around a woman that carries such a sexual aura.
This is the lady.
